title: Pumpkin cupcakes
ingredients: ['280g plain flour', '1 teaspoon ground cinnamon', '1/2 teaspoon ground nutmeg', '1/2 teaspoon ground ginger', '1/2 teaspoon ground cloves', '1/2 teaspoon ground allspice', '1/2 teaspoon salt', '1 tablespoon baking powder', '1/2 teaspoon bicarbonate of soda', '110g butter, softened', '200g caster sugar', '5 tablespoons brown soft sugar', '2 eggs, room temperature', '180ml milk', '250g pumpkin, cooked and pureed', 'Cinnamon cream cheese icing', '200g cream cheese, softened', '50g butter, softened', '350g icing sugar', '1 teaspoon vanilla extract', '1 teaspoon ground cinnamon']
